      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SUNSET CALIGULA (3) was a (29.66) winner last time out at this track from Box 6. Well placed and will be tough to beat. SUNSET CLARICE (1) has an excellent record over this course and distance having never missed the placings in nine starts, including four wins and five placings. Hit the frame latest (30.04) when second at this track in a Grade 4/5. With even luck and a clean start should be thereabouts. KING NANGAR (2) settled midfield in the run and boxed on to finish there when 5th (35.15) at this track. Solid record here at the distance winning five races. Has performed well from this box with a win and three minor placings to his name from five starts. Expected to feature in the finish. INTIMIDATION (7) must be included in calculations.",
